{% comment %}
  TipTop360 — Homepage Body Section v2
  ─────────────────────────────────────
  ✅ Meta title + description injection (inline JS — theme-agnostic)
  ✅ OG / Twitter card meta update
  ✅ JSON-LD: Organization · WebSite · Product (hero) · ItemList · FAQPage
  ✅ Hero image: fetchpriority=high, preload link, eager load
  ✅ All images: image_url filter, srcset + sizes, explicit width/height (no CLS)
  ✅ Fonts: preconnect, font-display swap via Google Fonts URL param
  ✅ CDN preconnect for faster asset resolution
  ✅ Cart drawer: AJAX, stays on page, qty controls, checkout CTA
  ✅ Variant selectors: color + age inline on card
  ✅ Sticky mobile CTA bar
  ✅ Mobile-first responsive, tight spacing
{% endcomment %}

